## GEMINI AI INTEGRATION RULES
- Use Gemini Flash for real-time responses (meal logging, quick questions)
- Use Gemini Pro for complex holistic insights (weekly reports, cross-module analysis)
- Always include user context in system prompt: goals, recent data summary, health conditions
- Cache common AI responses locally (Hive) with 24-hour TTL
- Rate limit client-side: max 30 requests/hour per user
- Never send raw PII to Gemini - anonymize where possible
- AI responses must include disclaimers: "This is not medical advice"
- Structure all AI prompts in `lib/services/ai_prompts/` as template strings

