## IMPORTANT REMINDERS
1. **Offline-first**: Every feature must work without internet. Sync when connected.
2. **Repository pattern**: Never bypass it. This is your migration insurance.
3. **Feature flags**: Use Firebase Remote Config to toggle incomplete features.
4. **No medical claims**: AI insights use language like "consider", "you may want to", never "you should" or "you have".
5. **Privacy**: Encrypt health data at rest. Implement DPDPA-compliant data export/deletion.
6. **Battery**: GPS tracking must use battery-efficient modes. Test on real devices.
7. **Indian food focus**: Food database must have comprehensive Indian cuisine coverage.
